**[MEDIUM] `stats_models/src/lib.rs`:121-129 – Redundant manual rank calculation.**
The code manually calculates the rank of the matrix by inspecting the diagonal of `R`. The `faer::ColPivQr` object already provides a `rank()` method that does this. Using the built-in method is simpler, less error-prone, and ensures consistency with `faer`'s internal logic.

